@NODE Install "ITime.Guide: Installation"
The  Installation  is really easy!  Just place it to anywhere, where you can
find it again.  That's all..  Easy..  isn't it?
@ENDNODE



@NODE About "ITime.Guide: Programdescription"
Programdescription:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
I programmed this little tool, because I needed a tool which can show me the
gone  time  since  I  have  logged  to the internet.  Btw, I couln't look to
T*lleUhr anymore and so I decided to include a normal clock to ITime.
@ENDNODE



